    <briefdescription>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Manages pb_kit pushbuffers to prevent overflows and optimize resets.</para>
<para>In particular, this class manages the underlying pbkit begin/end block to transparently break large logical blocks into chunks under the max size allowed by pbkit. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
